'''Peshawar Fashion Week''' ('''PFW''') is an annually [[fashion week|fashion event]] held in [[Peshawar]], [[Pakistan]].<ref name=tribune2011>{{cite news|title=The fate of Peshawar Fashion Week|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/261562/the-fate-of-peshawar-fashion-week/|accessdate=March 5, 2013|newspaper=[[The Express Tribune]]|date=September 28, 2011}}</ref> It represents the [[Culture of Pakistan|culture]] of Pakistan, especially [[Khyber Pakhtunkhwa]]. Events is organised by the ''KHYBER PAKHTOONKHAW Fashion DESIGN and Arts Council'' (KPFDAC).<ref>{{cite news|title=Yet another fashion council|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/87551/make-way-for-peshawar-fashion-week/}}</ref> First event was held in 2011.<ref name="tribune2011" />
== 2011 == First PFW 2011 was scheduled to be held in September 2011 but for some reason KPFDAC delayed the event.<ref name="tribune2011" /> Venue was a private hotel in Peshawar.
== 2013 == PFW 2013 was held on March 4–5, 2013 in Peshawar.
